 id=\"acd-check3\" class=\"acd-check\" type=\"checkbox\">\n        <label class=\"acd-label\" for=\"acd-check3\">募集要項</label>\n        <div class=\"acd-content\">\n          <div class=\"acd-inner\">\n            <div class=\"cnavi08\"><a href=\"https://www.kurabun.co.jp/recruitment/graduate/\">新卒採用</a></div>\n            <div class=\"cnavi09\"><a href=\"https://www.kurabun.co.jp/recruitment/career/\">中途採用</a></div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </li>\n      <!-- <li class=\"js-link_match_location\"><a href=\"https://www.kurabun.co.jp/recruit/requirements/\">募集要項</a></li> -->\n      <li class=\"js-link_match_location\"><a href=\"https://www.kurabun.co.jp/recruit/faq/\">よくある質問</a></li>\n      <li class=\"entry-btn -graduate\"><a href=\"https://www.kurabun.co.jp/recruitment/graduate/\">新卒<br>ENTRY</a></li>\n      <li class=\"entry-btn -career\"><a href=\"https://www.kurabun.co.jp/recruit/entry/\">中途<br>ENTRY</a></li>\n    </ul>\n    \n  <!-- /grobal-navigation--></nav>\n<!-- /hamburger-menu --></div>\n\n</header>\n  <!-- ▲ header ====================================================== -->\n\n  <!-- ▼ title =================================== -->\n  <div class=\"page-title\">\n    <h1>環境への取り組み</h1>\n  </div>\n  <!-- ▲ title =================================== -->\n\n  <!-- ▼ topicpath =============================== -->\n    \n    <div class=\"topic-path\">\n      <ol>\n        <li><a href=\"https://www.kurabun.co.jp/recruit/\">ホーム</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"https://www.kurabun.co.jp/recruit/environmental-initiatives/\">環境への取り組み</a></li>\n        \n      </ol>\n    </div>\n    \n  <!-- ▲ topicpath =============================== -->\n\n  <!-- ▼ container =================================================== -->\n  <div class=\"container\">\n\n  <!-- ▼ content =========================================== -->\n  <div class=\"content\">\n    <div id=\"jsChangeContents\">\n\n      \n      <div class=\"inner\">\n        \n\n        \n        \n\n        \n\n        <div>\n          \n          <div class=\"acms-entry\">\n            <div class=\"acms-grid-r\">\n            \n\n\n\n<!-- テキスト -->\n\n<p class=\"copy\">環境問題が大きく注目されている昨今。クラブンも企業として、また個人としても環境に配慮した取り組みに力を入れています！！</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<!-- テキスト -->\n\n<h3 >ISO14001</h3>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"js-unit_group-align acms-entry-unit-full acms-col-sm-6\">\n\n<hr class=\"clearHidden\">\n\n\n\n\n\n<!-- 画像 -->\n<div class=\"column-image-left\">\n    <img\n      class=\"js-lazy-load columnImage\"\n      data-src=\"https://www.kurabun.co.jp/archives/017/202112/922c077e6835f5eb1f4ee2acd0ea0973.png\"\n      alt=\"\"\n      width=\"531\"\n      height=\"376\">\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"js-unit_group-align acms-entry-unit-full acms-col-sm-6\">\n\n\n<!-- テキスト -->\n\n<p>クラブン株式会社は、『地球に優しく、社会に優しく、人に優しく』をモットーに環境問題に積極的に取り組んでいます。社内の紙・ゴミ・電気の削減。<br />\n社外に対してもエコ商品など環境対応商品の切り替え提案も行い健全な環境の保全に努めています。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"/company/iso.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">詳しくはこちら</a></p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n</div>\n\n<hr class=\"clearHidden\">\n\n<!-- テキスト -->\n\n<h3 >SDGs</h3>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"js-unit_group-align acms-entry-unit-full acms-col-sm-6\">\n\n<hr class=\"clearHidden\">\n\n\n\n\n\n<!-- 画像 -->\n<div class=\"column-image-left\">\n    <img\n      class=\"js-lazy-load columnImage\"\n      data-src=\"https://www.kurabun.co.jp/archives/017/202111/1692a1dd553de2ddd3b310ea7b382ad1.png\"\n      alt=\"\"\n      width=\"531\"\n      height=\"376\">\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"js-unit_group-align acms-entry-unit-full acms-col-sm-6\">\n\n\n<!-- テキスト -->\n\n<p>SDGs（持続可能な開発目標）は、「誰一人取り残さない」をテーマにより良い社会の実現を目指す世界共通の目標です。<br />\nクラブンでは、SDGsの推進に繋がるノベルティ商品やLED照明などの環境配慮商品の販売、紙ごみ・段ボール・産業廃棄物の再資源化業者への委託など、環境への取り組みを行っております。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"/company/sdgs/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">詳しくはこちら</a></p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n</div>\n\n\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <hr class=\"clearHidden\">\n          \n          \n\n          \n\n          \n          \n\n        </div>\n\n        \n        </div>\n        \n      \n\n\n    <!-- /jsChangeContents --></div>\n  <!-- /content --></div>\n  <!-- ▲ content =========================================== -->\n\n  <!-- ▼ sidebar ==================================== -->\n  <ul class=\"recruit-lnavi\">\n  <li class=\"js-link_match_location\"><a href=\"https://www.kurabun.co.jp/recruit/data/\">数字で見るクラブン</a></li>\n  <li class=\"js-link_match_location\"><a href=\"https://www.kurabun.co.jp/recruit/personnelsystem/\">人事制度（教育制度）</a></li>\n  <li class=\"js-link_match_location\"><a href=\"https://www.kurabun.co.jp/recruit/club/\">同好会・部活動</a></li>\n  <li class=\"js-link_match_location\"><a href=\"https://www.kurabun.co.jp/recruit/base/\">各拠点紹介</a></li>\n  <li class=\"js-link_match_location\"><a href=\"https://www.kurabun.co.jp/recruit/walfare/\">福利厚生</a></li>\n  <li class=\"js-link_match_location\"><a href=\"https://www.kurabun.co.jp/recruit/csr/\">社会貢献活動</a></li>\n  <li class=\"js-link_match_location\"><a href=\"https://www.kurabun.co.jp/recruit/environmental-initiatives/\">環境への取り組み</a></li>\n</ul>\n  <!-- ▲ sidebar ==================================== -->\n\n  <!-- /container --></div>\n  <!-- ▲ container =================================================== -->\n\n\n  <!-- ▼ footer ====================================================== -->\n  \n<div class=\"instagram-btn\">\n  <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/kurabun__saiyou/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img src=\"/theme